</div>

<div class="zm-item-answer-detail">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


知乎用户

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="83">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$wang-ze-xu-16" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/wang-ze-xu-16" class="zg-link" title="王泽旭">王泽旭</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$gu-xiao-yan-69-15" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/gu-xiao-yan-69-15" class="zg-link" title="顾笑嫣">顾笑嫣</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$qing-zheng-hong-cha" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/qing-zheng-hong-cha" class="zg-link" title="清蒸红茶">清蒸红茶</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="3072078" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">爱来不来如果还去了，她要的一定是饭，不是你。


</div>

